comment1.text=\n\ Pre-loads\ all\ game\ sounds\ into\ RAM.\n\ Must\ be\ called\ ONCE\ before\ any\ sound\ is\ played.\n\ Each\ sound\ is\ play()ed\ and\ immediately\ stop()ped\ to\ force\ Greenfoot\n\ to\ decode\ it,\ eliminating\ first-play\ lag\ spikes.\n
